languages.text:
The Cyber-Eagle has left the battlefield and can't be targeted by any attacks or abilities. It restores 33% Wounds at the start of each round.
While the Cyber-Eagle is {g|f:ec56854df2e84ef196a49079a43b5211}Ascended{/g}, the Overseer can use alternative varants of its abilities.
